name: Mike Goldberg
summary: Experienced full-stack developer. I've worked on greenfield projects for leading companies such as Samsung, ServiceNow, and The Daily. I've worked in advertising, news media, product development, streaming video, and enterprise software. I've worked individually, or on agile/cross-functional teams, to complete websites, web apps, and prototypes.
